<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.321914>
    dc:description "Figs. 3 – 10. Syringophilopsis polioptilus sp. n., female (Figs. 3 – 7) and male (Figs. 8 – 10). Fig. 3. Hypostomal apex. Fig. 4. Peritremes. Figs. 5, 6. Cuticular striation around bases of seta d 2. Fig. 7. Fan-like seta p’ of leg III. Fig. 8. Dorsal view. Fig. 9. Peritreme. Fig. 10. Posterior part of opisthosoma in ventral view. Scale lines 20 µm (Figs. 3, 4, 7, 9), 50 µm (Figs. 5, 6), 100 µm (Figs. 8, 10)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/321914/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.321918>
    dc:description "Figs. 1, 2. Syringophilopsis polioptilus sp. n., female. Fig. 1. Dorsal view. Fig. 2. Ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/321918/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

